        {
            "title": "Anthropic年度經常性收入飆升至190億美元 Claude Code表現強勁",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/GQcDb8ntU.u8og0ujZxDlw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEAB20CL_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:Anthropic;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/Anthropic\">Anthropic</a>預計將創造超過190億美元的年度收入,其中僅2月份就新增60億美元,執行長Dario Amodei在摩根士丹利TMT會議上證實了這一消息。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這一預測使該人工智慧公司的營收運行率較去年底增長超過一倍。新的年度經常性收入目標從2025年底的90億美元,以及幾週前的約140億美元大幅上升。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彭博新聞首先報導了這一發展。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">營收運行率的增長主要得益於Anthropic旗下人工智慧模型和產品的採用,包括其編碼工具Claude Code。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-5cc1385b-571a-372d-8e99-e73c2baf55ef-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Anthropic目前估值達3,800億美元,今年勢頭強勁。該公司的產品因能協助自動化任務而備受關注,其中包括Claude Code。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Anthropic與五角大廈在人工智慧安全措施上的衝突,目前為該公司業務蒙上陰影。週五,國防部長Pete Hegseth宣布該人工智慧開發商為供應鏈風險,這一名稱通常保留給美國視為對手國家的公司。此舉源於一場對峙,Anthropic要求限制五角大廈將其人工智慧技術用於監控和自主武器。Hegseth的聲明旨在切斷Anthropic與美國政府及其他公司的銷售往來。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據投資者Brad Gerstner的說法,Amodei在活動上表示:「我們相信美國,我們相信協助保衛我們的國家……將繼續努力與國防部找出解決方案。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/anthropic%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%A6%E7%B6%93%E5%B8%B8%E6%80%A7%E6%94%B6%E5%85%A5%E9%A3%86%E5%8D%87%E8%87%B3190%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83-claude-code%E8%A1%A8%E7%8F%BE%E5%BC%B7%E5%8B%81-154028567.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-04 23:52:44",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "大摩:三星股價回調時買入",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/qrLfpDVeT_YXZ61lumkxXg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA7R04R_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 根據<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:摩根士丹利;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/摩根士丹利\">摩根士丹利</a>分析師Shawn Kim的說法,三星電子股價在近期拋售後看起來頗具吸引力,他表示此次回調為投資者在AI記憶體架構重大轉變前創造了買入機會。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">摩根士丹利指出,該股本週迄今已下跌約20%,而KOSPI指數則下跌17%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Kim寫道,隨著晶片變得更加專業化,AI推理的記憶體市場正朝著混合模式發展。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">雖然HBM繼續佔據主導地位,但摩根士丹利表示:\"SRAM正在為延遲比吞吐量密度更重要的工作負載開闢利基市場。\"</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-219b27d2-c206-36ed-9d41-fe6e3780386e-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該公司預計,英偉達將在即將舉行的GPU技術大會上推出一款新的推理晶片,採用圍繞大量片上SRAM構建的語言處理單元架構。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">摩根士丹利表示,該架構\"專為推理的順序速度而設計\",吸引那些\"願意為速度付費\"的客戶。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據Kim的說法,爭論的焦點不是SRAM與HBM的對比,而是兩者如何\"保持層次結構,將SRAM用於熱路徑執行,將HBM用於可擴展的記憶體容量。\"</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">重要的是,摩根士丹利補充道,LPU設計可以繞過\"當前HBM和CoWoS封裝的供應鏈瓶頸\"。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管AI記憶體市場最終如何分化存在不確定性,但該公司仍將三星電子列為首選股,理由是HBM4認證、SRAM能力、晶圓代工靈活性以及更廣泛的商品上行週期。摩根士丹利還重申了對SK海力士的正面看法。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Kim寫道:\"從歷史上看,這種回調提供了良好的買入機會\",並補充說盈利預期仍有\"很大的復甦空間\"。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
